How I Got These Answers
I used SQL to clean messy data and find patterns:
•	Fixed company names that were spelled multiple ways
•	Converted dates so I could track trends month by month
•	Used window functions to rank companies by how deeply they cut
•	Bucketed funding amounts into meaningful groups
